name: Fuck the dollar, give me your tezos - PART 5
description:
How nice to meet again in a new edition of FTD !!! .... On this occasion, our dear family needed to take a vacation, what better place to go on vacation than Disney World?
Ernie, Tomy the human centipede, Michael Jackson, The man with a brown mask that we still don't know his name, Mickey and Minnie, well, the whole family.
Thanks to everyone who came out to see this shit. FTD Part 5 is free to buyers of Tomy the Human Centipede and Michael Jackson, I hope you enjoy it. A big kiss, Matias.
